app/
├── +layout.tsx               ← Global app layout (wraps everything)
├── (tabs)/                   ← Tab navigation group
│   ├── +layout.tsx           ← Tab layout (bottom tabs setup)
│   ├── index.tsx             ← Home tab screen
│   └── profile/              ← Profile tab
│       ├── [id].tsx          ← Dynamic profile screen
│       └── +layout.tsx       ← Optional layout just for Profile tab
├── _auth/                    ← Screens outside tabs (Splash, Create Account)
│   ├── +layout.tsx           ← Layout specific to auth screens
│   ├── _splash.tsx           ← Splash screen
│   └── _create-account.tsx   ← Create account screen
└── settings.tsx              ← A standalone screen outside tab and auth flow
